{"tid":1967430,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 11新機成日lag","createTime":"2020-04-11T02:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T08:29:20.000Z","uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83b24a7ded88e5caf883097a7df8dab662d9d9a6","tid":1967430,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:33:11.000Z","msg":"小弟老母前兩日換咗部新機 本身就用緊iphone x嘅<br />\n都係用返ios本身過資料嗰舊嘢 但係本身iphone x順暢冇問題嘅apps喺iphone11就會閃退 eg: pages 之類個啲<br />\n<br />\nSorry講到有啲1999咁 但呢個係根據我老母個描述講返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPages係我老母處理佢嗰啲工作嘅文件用嘅 唔知係咪過資料嗰陣有缺失定係啲文件多得滯搞到部機load唔到 佢話有啲文件係load唔到出嚟 同埋好多時候一㩒入去成部機就郁唔到 淨係可以彈返出主畫面<br />\n<br />\n加上我唔係佢部手機嘅用家 所以唔知道問題出係邊<br />\nVersion係ios 13.3.1  唔知有冇連登仔幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd6eeff73dc7b1f22fec2c3d1d1cfc23ead97c6","tid":1967430,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:37:33.000Z","msg":"題外話 琴日老母去撚左apple store搵嗰啲藍精靈睇吓邊度出問題 點撚知啲藍精靈直接幫佢reboot 再用舊果部iPhone x過啲資料落去 然後部機都係咁撚樣lag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後藍精靈話係我老母裝嗰啲apps嘅問題 然後就唔撚理我老母<br />\n<br />\n如果嗰陣我在場嘅話已經剷鳩佢 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dca4b7183ed94c3da58a5df0d786c186fe1ea8d","tid":1967430,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"老母已經喺度發脾氣發咗兩三日<br />\n有冇巴打救到我<br />\n唔想今晚又要落街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9083ee046803736a0f12beeb71724825df5fd1d","tid":1967430,"uid":38891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"所有apple問題一律係用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc4872fbe976da2301321f2fbf0ca7c29970bdb","tid":